The paper focuses on the understandability of spreadsheets, which is a software engineering concern, making cs.SE the most likely category. The paper also discusses metrics for measuring understandability, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) or human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The experiments conducted in the paper involve manipulating data in spreadsheets, which could be considered a data management task (cs.DB). Finally, the paper could also be relevant to cybernetics (cs.CY) as it deals with the interaction between humans and computer systems.
